HEADWORD: Ticketing
<hw>Tick"et*ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A periodical sale of ore in the
English mining districts; -- so called from the tickets upon which are
written the bids of the buyers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ticking</ent>⟦br⟧
